<A>__{the spy plane's long flimsy wings weren't made for dogfighting. they bend terribly in the rollout. and then the first missile streaks past, tries to correct its miss, but can't and vanishes into the distance at a 90 degree angle.}
<L>__{interior u 2 continuous}
<A>__{anderson's breath comes faster and faster as the second missile rises up, now visible. he puts the throttle as far as it goes, trying to outrun death. every second is a tenth of a mile, and every mile shortens the missile's life span. the rising missile drafts aft, closing on the u 2 from behind.}
